sequenceDiagram
    participant EvalHub as eval-hub Service
    participant Adapter as GarakAdapter<br/>(Batch Job Pod)
    participant Garak as Garak CLI<br/>(Subprocess)
    participant Target as Target LLM<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Judge as Judge LLM<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Attacker as Attacker LLM<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Evaluator as Evaluator LLM<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SDGLLM as SDG LLM<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFP as KFP API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over EvalHub,OCI: Flow 1: Simple Mode Scan
    EvalHub->>Adapter: JobSpec (ConfigMap mount)<br/>ServiceAccount
    Adapter->>Adapter: Resolve config (profile + overrides)
    Adapter->>Garak: Build & execute CLI command<br/>os.setsid process group
    Garak->>Target: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    Target-->>Garak: Response
    Garak-->>Adapter: JSONL/AVID results (filesystem)
    Adapter->>Adapter: Parse results, compute TBSA scoring
    Adapter->>OCI: Push scan artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Registry creds
    Adapter->>MLflow: Log experiment & artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    Adapter->>EvalHub: Report JobResults (callback)

    Note over EvalHub,OCI: Flow 2: KFP Mode Scan
    EvalHub->>Adapter: JobSpec (ConfigMap mount)
    Adapter->>S3: Upload config.json (redacted)<br/>TLS 1.2+ | AWS IAM
    Adapter->>KFP: Submit 6-step pipeline<br/>TLS 1.2+ | SA Token
    KFP->>KFP: validate step
    KFP->>S3: resolve_taxonomy artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+ | AWS IAM
    KFP->>SDGLLM: sdg_generate prompts<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    SDGLLM-->>KFP: Generated adversarial prompts
    KFP->>KFP: prepare_prompts step
    KFP->>Target: garak_scan step<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    Target-->>KFP: Scan results
    KFP->>S3: Upload scan results<br/>TLS 1.2+ | AWS IAM
    KFP-->>Adapter: Pipeline complete (poll)
    Adapter->>S3: Download results<br/>TLS 1.2+ | AWS IAM
    Adapter->>OCI: Push artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Registry creds

    Note over EvalHub,OCI: Flow 3: Intents Pipeline (Simple Mode)
    Adapter->>SDGLLM: Generate adversarial prompts from taxonomy<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token (SDG_API_KEY)
    SDGLLM-->>Adapter: SDG output
    Adapter->>Adapter: Build intent stubs & typology files
    Adapter->>Garak: Execute with multi-probe config
    Garak->>Target: Scan prompts<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    Garak->>Judge: Response evaluation<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token (JUDGE_API_KEY)
    Garak->>Attacker: Tree-of-attacks generation<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token (ATTACKER_API_KEY)
    Garak->>Evaluator: Attack scoring<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token (EVALUATOR_API_KEY)
    Garak-->>Adapter: Multi-probe results
    Adapter->>Adapter: Generate ART HTML report (Jinja2 + Vega)
